Modified DeviceSerialPort.cpp, and made a Makefile.

To run DeviceSerialPort, you need to do something like:
export GENICAM_ROOT=/opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/
export GENICAM_ROOT_V2_4=/opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/
sudo mkdir /opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/xml
sudo touch /opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/xml/CommunicationGEV.xml
sudo touch /opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/xml/CommunicationU3V.xml
sudo touch /opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/xml/ParametersGEV.xml
sudo touch /opt/pleora/ebus_sdk/Ubuntu-12.04-x86_64/xml/ParametersU3V.xml
